Wolfblade::

She smiled at him as he pulled her towards him. She leaned her head
back against his shoulder. "Are you sure? I don't want to keep from
'other' duties." Her tone of voice slight sting in it. She turned and
put her arms around his neck. "Alright love, we can stay out here a
bit longer if you want."  She kissed him and let the mech fluid rush
to her head. 







--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, robert riley <bustercross365@y...> wrote:
> Malice:
>  
> He sighed a bit as the base came into view.  He wasn't ready to go
back just yet.  He wanted more time with Wolfblade, it was much
simpler out here, it was just him and her, with some minor annoyances.
 He pulled her close and put his arms around her.
>  
> "We can get something later, let's stay out a bit more, I want to be
with you alone right now."
